storm nimbus
    Run this on one node.

storm supervisor
    Run this on all nodes.

./compile_java.sh
    Compiles Java code and builds a jar.

storm jar <name>.jar <ClassName>
    For local execution

storm jar <name>.jar <ClassName> <topologyName>
    For submission to Storm cluster.

http://demeter.inf.ed.ac.uk/cross/stormcpp.html
    For C++ integration.
